ent can be predicted up to 720\nms ahead of a potential fall with an average precision greater than 0.95 and an\naverage F-score of 0.82. Finally, we validate our approach in real-time by\ndeploying it on a legged robot and switching its gait mode based on slip event\ndetection.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 30 Jul 2022 23:37:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-08-02"}
